# Big5Loop Repository Rule

## Canonical Repository

**ALWAYS use:** https://github.com/jahua/Big5Loop

## Git Operations

- **Local path:** `CareLoop/` (under thesis project root — folder not yet renamed)
- **Remote:** `origin` → `https://github.com/jahua/Big5Loop.git`
- **Push:** Always push Big5Loop changes to `github.com/jahua/Big5Loop`, NOT to `thesis-papeer`
- **Clone:** `git clone https://github.com/jahua/Big5Loop.git`

## Important

1. Big5Loop is a **separate git repository** nested inside the thesis project
2. Changes to `CareLoop/` should be committed and pushed within the CareLoop directory
3. The thesis-papeer repo tracks CareLoop as a directory but Big5Loop has its own git history
4. When asked to push Big5Loop changes, always `cd CareLoop && git push origin main`

## Quick Reference

```bash
# Push Big5Loop changes
cd CareLoop && git add -A && git commit -m "message" && git push origin main

# Check Big5Loop remote
cd CareLoop && git remote -v
# Should show: origin https://github.com/jahua/Big5Loop.git
```
